<%# app/views/inquiry_mailer/new_inquiry_alert.text.erb %>
New Inquiry Received
====================

A new inquiry has been submitted to The Anchorpoint Retreat.

GUEST INFORMATION
-----------------
Name:         <%= @inquiry.name %>
Email:        <%= @inquiry.email %>
Phone:        <%= @inquiry.phone.presence || "N/A" %>
Company:      <%= @inquiry.company.presence || "N/A" %>
Retreat Type: <%= @inquiry.retreat_type.presence&.titleize || "N/A" %>

INQUIRY DETAILS
---------------
Preferred Dates: <%= @inquiry.preferred_dates.presence || "N/A" %>
Group Size:      <%= @inquiry.group_size.presence || "N/A" %>

Message:
<%= @inquiry.message %>

---
This is an automated notification. Please respond to the guest within 24-48 hours.
